description: The people of Portland are going nuts over the delicious food and friendly service that they always find at Gourmet On The Go. Chef Geoff, with the help of his father and a few of his friends, built this big blue truck so that he could share his talent for crafting tasty all-American classics with the streets of PDX. His burgers, sliders, sandwiches, and sausages are built with the finest ingredients and are all so amazingly flavorful. That’s not even all, for sides, you’ve got hand-punched fries and crisp and crunchy coleslaw. With its caliber of quality, this truck has gained innumerable fans, so if you wish to excite your guests at your next event with some of the tastiest food around, definitely go with Gourmet On The Go.
name: Gourmet On The Go
